name: [Identity] Base
background: A W-Engine with a component structure adjusted according to specific parameters. It can enhance the defensive capabilities of those who have a certain style of combat. If the user does not meet the requirements for this W-Engine, then carrying it would be like lugging around an over-sized shield in battle.
skill: When attacked, equipper's DEF increases by 20%/23%/26%/29%/32% for 8s.
